Package energy.usef.agr.dto.device.capability

JSON classes of aggregator device capabilities.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeviceCapabilityDto
    JSON class representing the capability of a UDI device.
    IncreaseCapabilityDto
    JSON class for the increase capability of a UDI device.
    InterruptCapabilityDto
    JSON class representing an interrupt capability of a UDI device.
    ProfileDto
    JSON Object to have a list of profiles.
    ReduceCapabilityDto
    JSON class representing a reduce capability of a UDI device.
    ReportCapabilityDto
    JSON class representing a report capability of a UDI device.
    ShiftCapabilityDto
    JSON class representing a shift capability of a UDI device.
    UdiEventDto
    DTO class for the Udi Event objects.
    VariationCapabilityDto
    Abstract entity representing a variation capability (increase or reduce) of a UDI device.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    InterruptCapabilityTypeDto
    JSON Enumeration of the various InterruptCapability types.
    UdiEventTypeDto
    DTO enumeration of the Udi Event types.
